  • Method Details

    • updateSchema

      public void updateSchema(VectorAccessible batch)
      Description copied from class: SplunkBatchWriter
      Update the schema in RecordWriter. Called before starting writing the records. In this case, we add the index to Splunk here. Splunk's API is a little sparse and doesn't really do much in the way of error checking or providing feedback if the operation fails.
      Specified by:
      updateSchema in interface RecordWriter
      Overrides:
      updateSchema in class SplunkBatchWriter
